OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FPolice have insisted they did not
OL,7,F"fail" a woman who was murdered by her
OL,8,Fviolent ex-partner after he was
OL,9,Freleased on bail despite a long
OL,10,Fhistory of abusing her.
OL,12,FVincent Morgan was the subject of his
OL,13,Fthird domestic violence protection
OL,14,Forder (DVPO) and was banned from
OL,15,Fcontacting Lisa Welford when he
OL,16,Fdrowned her on 24 April.
