OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FShe added: "It absolutely infuriates
OL,7,Fme. These deaths can be prevented.
OL,8,FLisa's death could have easily been
OL,9,Fprevented.
OL,11,F"She has obviously been on the
OL,12,Fpolice's radar for quite a while for
OL,13,Fthem to have implemented domestic
OL,14,Fviolence protection orders. It shows
OL,15,Fthat there has been some serious
OL,16,Fincidents before she tragically lost
OL,17,Fher life."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
