OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FBut Det Ch Insp Shaun Page, who led
OL,7,Fthe investigation, defended the
OL,8,Fhandling of the case. He said: "North
OL,9,FYorkshire Police didn't fail to
OL,10,Fprotect (Ms Welford).
OL,12,F"We were aware of previous incidents
OL,13,Finvolving Lisa and Vincent Morgan, but
OL,14,Fthose are now subject of an IOPC
OL,15,Finvestigation. But the investigation
OL,16,Fhas led to a conviction for murder and
OL,17,Fwe are pleased with the sentence today
OL,18,Fat court."
