OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FHe added: "North Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Ftakes domestic abuse exceptionally
OL,8,Fseriously. We have a specialist team
OL,9,Fthat supports victims.
OL,11,F"As in this case, anybody at the end
OL,12,Fof a relationship, looking to leave a
OL,13,Fdomestic abuse relationship, can be at
OL,14,Fexceptional risk of harm and I would
OL,15,Fask them to think about reaching out
OL,16,Fto us, the police, or another agency."
OL,18,FHe said police would try to prosecute
OL,19,Fperpetrators even without the support
OL,20,Fof victims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
