OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FMorgan's trial heard he was described
OL,7,Fby a previous partner as violent and
OL,8,Fcontrolling and had a long history of
OL,9,Fphysical abuse towards Ms Welford.
OL,11,FHe was under investigation for
OL,12,Fassaulting her in February at the time
OL,13,Fof the murder.
OL,15,FOn the day of the attack Morgan spent
OL,16,Fthe day with Ms Welford, despite being
OL,17,Fbanned from contacting her.
OL,19,FThey drank together, ending up on the
OL,20,Fbank of the River Derwent in the
OL,21,Fcentre of Malton at around 11.30pm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
