OL,3,CPolice deny failing woman drowned by
OL,4,Cbailed abuser
OL,6,FPolice were alerted by witnesses who
OL,7,Fsaw Ms Welford in the water.
OL,9,FShe had suffered a cardiac arrest and
OL,10,Fhad no detectable pulse when she was
OL,11,Fpulled out of the water.
OL,13,FProsecutor Craig Hassall said Morgan
OL,14,Fcontradicted himself after being
OL,15,Farrested.
OL,17,FHe said: "In the ambulance he said she
OL,18,Fhad deliberately entered the water and
OL,19,Ftook own life, and then said shortly
OL,20,Fafter she had slipped on the bank and
OL,21,Fthat's why she was in the water."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
