OL,6,FSentencing Morgan, Recorder of Leeds
OL,7,FJudge Guy Kearl told him: "Over the
OL,8,Fpast two decades you have shown
OL,9,Fyourself to be a person who is
OL,10,Fviolent, particularly when intoxicated
OL,11,Fwith alcohol or drugs.
OL,13,F"When in drink you are brutal and
OL,14,Fcallous, unable to control your desire
OL,15,Ffor violence towards your partners."
